ğŸ“Š Sample SQL Queries

The following queries can be run on the patient_visits table:

ğŸ”¹ View all patient visits
SELECT * FROM patient_visits;

ğŸ”¹ Total visits per patient
SELECT patient_id, SUM(visit_count) AS total_visits
FROM patient_visits
GROUP BY patient_id
ORDER BY total_visits DESC;

ğŸ”¹ Visits by facility
SELECT facility, COUNT(*) AS visits
FROM patient_visits
GROUP BY facility;

ğŸ”¹ Visits per day
SELECT visit_date, COUNT(*) AS visits
FROM patient_visits
GROUP BY visit_date
ORDER BY visit_date;

